{"title":"Wild new DJI FPV drone lets you control its flight by moving your hand, up to 87mph!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/02/wild-new-dji-fpv-drone-lets-you-control-its-flight-by-moving-your-hand-up-to-87mph/","date":1614693678000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>The all-new DJI FPV drone gives you more intuitive motion control and HD goggles, completely changing the way you fly and film from the air. It flies like a racing drone, hovers like a camera drone, and accelerate and stop faster than anything they’ve made before.</p><p>DJI has been making FPV (first person view) goggles for their drones for years, giving users an immersive view of what the drone sees, but speeds up the transmission for a virtually real-time, reliable transmission.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" alt=\"dji fpv drone\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 630w\" ezoid=\"0.10314027226123867\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-3-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 630w\"></a></p><p>Built around a combination of drone, goggles and controller, there are two things that immediately set the new DJI FPV apart from its siblings: The looks, and the optional Motion Controller.</p><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/LVoPGlNvHhw?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\"></iframe></span></p><h2>DJI FPV Drone Specs</h2><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1.jpg\" alt=\"people flying the dji fpv drone\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-flight-1-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Besides the bug-like spaceship looks, which allow the drone to hit speeds of up to 87mph (140km/h), accelerate 0-62mph (0-100km/h) in just 2 seconds, and fly more like a racing drone, the big differences are in the new flight modes and features.</p><p>Higher performance motors are used to allow better maneuverability, and they added an Emergency Brake feature that stops the drone in place and keeps it hovering.</p><p>Three flight modes are standard:</p><ul><li><strong>Normal (N) Mode:</strong>&nbsp;Similar to other DJI drones, allows hovering in place with the use of GPS and/or visual positioning systems (VPS) on the bottom of the drone. Front obstacle detection sensors issue warnings when you’re getting close to something, but the pilot has to fly away from the obstacles. Start here, then try…</li><li><strong>Sport (S) Mode:</strong>&nbsp;A new hybrid blend of M and N mode, S mode offers some of the Manual dynamic movement capabilities <em>and</em> some of the key safety features of N mode. It’s a baby step towards using…</li><li><strong>Manual (M) Mode:</strong>&nbsp;Gives you full control over the drone, all sensors and auto-hovering features are disabled.</li></ul><p>It has a 10km flight range while still delivering an HD feed to the goggles and using auto-switching dual frequencies with 50Mbps transmission rate and built-in anti-interference tech.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller.jpg\" alt=\"dji fpv drone\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-and-controller-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumo