r.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Drone-Camera-218x150.jpg 218w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Drone-Camera-696x483.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Drone-Camera-1068x741.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Drone-Camera-605x420.jpg 605w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Drone-Camera-100x70.jpg 100w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Drone-Camera.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Drone-Camera-297x206.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Drone-Camera-800x555.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Drone-Camera-120x83.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Drone-Camera-768x533.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Drone-Camera-218x150.jpg 218w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Drone-Camera-696x483.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Drone-Camera-1068x741.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Drone-Camera-605x420.jpg 605w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Drone-Camera-100x70.jpg 100w\"></a></p><p>The single-axis gimbal is a bit different than on the Mavic series’ 3-axis drones. This helps stabilize the footage, but gives it a more realistic tilting effect as you wind through the canyons (chasing womp rats, perhaps?).</p><p>The camera records up to 4K/60fps at 120Mbps, or slow it down to 1080p/120fps. It packs their RockSteady electronic stabilization to fix shaky footage, and even corrects the distortion typically found in wide angle lenses.</p><p>It has a 150º field of view, but definitely note (in the video above) the lack of horizon-leveling means flying sideways alongside the subject will give you a tilted video. While that can be cool for action, it suggests this done leans more toward sport use and capturing insane action than for videographers seeking the most control over their shots.</p><h3>DIJ FPV Goggles</h3><figure id=\"attachment_252304\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-252304\"><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-1.jpg\" alt=\"dji fpv drone goggles\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1748\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-1.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-1.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-1-297x260.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-1-800x699.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dji-fpv-drone-goggles-1-120x105.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoi