harging cable.&nbsp;The Fly More kit adds two more batteries and some accessories for $299 more.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control.jpg\" alt=\"dji fpv standard remote control\" width=\"1200\" height=\"448\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control-297x111.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control-800x299.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control-120x45.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control-768x287.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control-696x260.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control-1068x399.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control-1125x420.jpg 1125w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control-297x111.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control-800x299.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control-120x45.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control-768x287.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control-696x260.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control-1068x399.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-standard-Remote-Control-1125x420.jpg 1125w\"></a></p><p>The standard (included) controller has an interesting button layout, but it’s the optional $199 Motion Controller that you’ll really want to add…</p><h3>DJI FPV Motion Controller</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Motion-Sensor-Remote-Controller-joystick.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Motion-Sensor-Remote-Controller-joystick.jpg\" alt=\"dji fpv motion controller remote joystick shown from different angles\" width=\"2000\" height=\"913\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Motion-Sensor-Remote-Controller-joystick.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DJI-FPV-Motion-Sensor-Remote-Controller-joystick.jpg 2000